    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="948451144">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-948451144" class="vote-count">5</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-948451144" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="948451144">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nulland/">NULLAND</a>
                    <span>2015-08-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">枯燥，缺乏血肉。苍白空洞。而且四处引用不值得推敲的其它国家汉学家的观点，不堪卒读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="957769754">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-957769754" class="vote-count">4</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-957769754" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="957769754">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1140109/">魏晓波</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-09-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">500块钱，镇家之宝，还有几本没读完。这套书里有大量的数据和文献资料，不是故事会风格的。文革结束后，这本书上没有都说好，提到了新的社会问题，比如年轻人开始对政治和高层反感，失去了参与政治的热情。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="636507424">
