  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="27604683">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/roadliu/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46958026-6.jpg" alt="路德" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27604683/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27604683/" class="">第50页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/roadliu/" class=" " title="路德">路德</a>
                (独立之精神，自由之思想)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27604683">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">群雄逐鹿，比拼的是人才、人口、土地、资源、地缘优势、制度设计和历史际遇，过份强调领导者的个人素质、眼光与决心实在是一件误导人的事。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27604683/">(<span class="">7回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-15 21:07</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                群雄逐鹿，比拼的是人才、人口、土地、资源、地缘优势、制度设计和历史际遇，过份强调领导者的个人素质、眼光与决心实在是一件误导人的事。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

